OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold start once again, but
OL,6,Fwith early frost and some patchy low
OL,7,Fcloud soon clearing to leave another
OL,8,Fdry and bright day. Warmer than
OL,9,FThursday with light winds, but cooler
OL,10,Fnear the coast where some low cloud
OL,11,Fcould linger.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry and largely clear
OL,14,Fovernight. Temperatures falling to
OL,15,Fagain give a slight risk of some rural
OL,16,Ffrost, and the potential for some mist
OL,17,Fand fog patches by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
