OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,6,Fexpected, but likely cloudier and with
OL,7,Fa fresher breeze, particularly towards
OL,8,Fthe east coast. Temperatures feeling
OL,9,Fcooler as a result.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith some hazy sunshine Sunday after
OL,13,Fany early low cloud clears, warm for
OL,14,Fmost. Monday sees a risk of some heavy
OL,15,Fshowers. Drier again into Tuesday but
OL,16,Fturning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
